messages.message:
Hello! FYI that for this next release the following apps will have a deprecated tag on them in the product and will also be marked as deprecated in the release notes:
-Data Manager
-Encrypted Drive
-Form
-Lens
-Recipe book
-Report
-Sequencer
-Table Refiner
-Visual Refiner
-Viz

Being deprecated means they will be removed from the product in a future release, timing TBD.
